    "analyticsDigest": "Stickiness at 14.1% shows revisits are working, but ARPU of $0.03 (below cohort) signals that traffic-to-revenue conversion is blocked. Session time of 3m 05s (P75) indicates high engagement — room for premium conversion exists.\nMRR of $246 is only 16% of target — unreachable with ads alone. A new revenue model must come first.",
